An HR company with the most diverse talent pool in NZ, it connects highly skilled migrants and returning Kiwis, who are looking for jobs, with companies whose work culture has inclusion and diversity values. To  serve the diversified market of NZ, companies need a diversified team. WeaveTalent is a platform developed using MVC .Net and SQL DB, it provides ways of integration, career resources, assigned mentors and searchable candidates database.

It's my vision is that WeaveTalent helps skilled migrants integrate into NZ workforce both building a better community and economy for all.
